Hi there! It's great to hear that you're interested in managing your ad account with us. While we don't assign dedicated account managers, you can manage your ads and access various features through our Ad Manager platform. You can grant access to other users for your ad accounts if needed. For more details on how to manage your account, check out this guide: [Account Management Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17539290349709-Account-Management-Guide).
